{"tid":1990391,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【上車之選】離島樓價平，坪洲最快25分鐘出中環","createTime":"2020-04-26T15:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T02:43:07.000Z","uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a90e0e8128a890497c7a35b5db0ffdb98b273de0","tid":1990391,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.reubird.hk/large%2Fblogs%2FPeng-Chau%2Fpc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.reubird.hk%2Flarge%252Fblogs%252FPeng-Chau%252Fpc3.jpg&h=bf9f90a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環番工既巴絲，有得唸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係船費貴d lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n坪洲環境清幽 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最快25分鐘出中環</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若怕長洲假日人多，可選擇坪洲，環境相對清幽。雖然坪洲班次較長洲疏，但是船程較短。平日上午時段，坪洲往中環碼頭約15至45分鐘一班船，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高速船最快25分鐘可到達中環碼頭</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">普通船約40分鐘</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n美達地產客戶經理劉寶珠指出，最近市道差，坪洲睇樓情況已經不像之前般熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n睇樓人士以30至40歲年輕人及退休人士為主，當中不乏上車客。她指準買家睇村屋多，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一個建築面積約350平方呎的單位，最平$190萬有交易</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2627474/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E4%B9%8B%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E9%9B%A2%E5%B3%B6%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%B9%B3%20%E5%9D%AA%E6%B4%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB25%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2627474%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%25B9%25B3%2520%25E5%259D%25AA%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB25%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4H6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=e6df762d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2627474/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%E4%B9%8B%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E9%9B%A2%E5%B3%B6%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%B9%B3%20%E5%9D%AA%E6%B4%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB25%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e91a73f8b58b77f9d93570d731a8a34ab63dfea","tid":1990391,"uid":89349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.reubird.hk/large%2Fblogs%2FPeng-Chau%2Fpc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.reubird.hk%2Flarge%252Fblogs%252FPeng-Chau%252Fpc3.jpg&h=bf9f90a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8891e480e12f872fdb3ff39143706f6db898630f","tid":1990391,"uid":128594,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"村屋都要得200尺唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b44fbb1d64f60b367ab69c9f62babe67c87e0af","tid":1990391,"uid":128594,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8891e480e12f872fdb3ff39143706f6db898630